column16: Mike Lowell pops out to first baseman Rhyne Hughes in foul territory.
Kevin Youkilis homers (3) on a fly ball to left field.   Dustin Pedroia scores.    Victor Martinez scores.
Jose Lopez pops out to shortstop Cesar Izturis.
Eric Byrnes walks.    Jack Wilson to 2nd.
Chone Figgins flies out to left fielder Lou Montanez.
Ichiro Suzuki flies out to center fielder Adam Jones.
Jack Wilson singles on a line drive to left fielder Lou Montanez.
Rob Johnson called out on strikes.
Casey Kotchman doubles (4) on a line drive to right fielder Nick Markakis.    Franklin Gutierrez scores.    Jose Lopez to 3rd.
Ken Griffey flies out to right fielder Nick Markakis.
Jose Lopez singles on a ground ball to left fielder Lou Montanez.    Franklin Gutierrez to 2nd.
Daric Barton pops out to shortstop Cesar Izturis.
Rajai Davis grounds out, second baseman Ty Wigginton to first baseman Garrett Atkins.    Cliff Pennington to 3rd.
Cliff Pennington doubles (3) on a line drive to left fielder Nolan Reimold.    Travis Buck scores.
Adam Rosales called out on strikes.
